data.title: Şehzade Mehmed Ertuğrul
data.meta_description: Şehzade Mehmed Ertuğrul Efendi was an Ottoman prince, the only son of Sultan Mehmed VI and his second consort Müveddet Kadın. He was the last child of Mehmed and his only son.
